  "I am a Software Engineer with a strong background in Full-Stack development, specializing in Backend Architecture and system scalability. I am passionate about modernizing legacy systems and designing solutions that drive operational efficiency.": "我是一名具有丰富Full-Stack开发经验的软件工程师，专注于后端架构和系统可扩展性。我热衷于现代化遗留系统和设计推动运营效率的解决方案。",
  "I am a Software Engineer specializing in Full-Stack development and System Architecture, with solid experience since 2017 developing scalable, high-performance solutions for the oil & gas and logistics sectors.\nI have advanced expertise in Java (Spring Boot), JavaScript/TypeScript (Node, React), and SQL. My experience includes modernizing legacy systems and designing microservices architectures, leveraging technologies like Docker, Kubernetes, and PostgreSQL to build robust and efficient environments.": "我是一名专注于Full-Stack开发和系统架构的软件工程师，自2017年以来在石油天然气和物流领域拥有开发可扩展、高性能解决方案的丰富经验。\n我在Java (Spring Boot)、JavaScript/TypeScript (Node, React)和SQL方面拥有高级专业知识。我的经验包括现代化遗留系统和设计微服务架构，利用Docker、Kubernetes和PostgreSQL等技术构建稳健高效的环境。",
